      "id": "971877198889426",
      "score": 4,
      "review_title": "amazing",
      "review_description": "Gas N Cars VR is one of the funniest and most entertaining VR games I’ve played in a while. Running the gas station, washing cars, filling up fuel, and dealing with complete chaos makes the game super addictive. The VR controls feel smooth and make everything way more immersive, especially when customers start piling in and things get hectic. I love how random and chaotic the gameplay can get — it never gets boring. Definitely a 5-star game if you enjoy funny sandbox-style VR games with lots to do!",
      "date": 1779919214,
      "review_helpful_count": 89,
      "author_display_name": "george2604",
      "author_alias": "george2604",
      "developer_response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "1218874141300773",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Pump that Chaos! ⛽💥",
      "review_description": "Gas N Cars is pure arcade chaos—a hilariously fast-paced petrol station sim where every customer is a wild card. Whether they’re trying to rob you, handing over fake cash, or just swerving all over the road after you slip them mushrooms, this game never lets up.\nThe sheer creativity in the mechanics is what sells it: extract a wheel to stop a thief, pour extra petrol to scam a customer, or just go full villain and watch the chaos unfold. The customer review system adds a fun moral choice—be a saint or a scammer?\nWith smooth controls, excellent polish, and a solid progression system, Gas N Cars is a hidden gem in the arcade world. If you love chaotic fun with quirky charm, this is a must-play. Just don’t be surprised if you crack up at the absurdity! 🚗💨⛽",
      "date": 1780180233,
      "review_helpful_count": 11,
      "author_display_name": "metaquesta99",
      "author_alias": "metaquesta99",
      "developer_response": null
    },
